<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            /* Modern dark gradient background with a subtle tech mesh pattern */
            background-color: #0d1117;
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(at 0% 0%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15) 0, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 100% 100%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0, transparent 50%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #c9d1d9;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            /* Semi-transparent glassmorphism effect */
            background: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 0;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px dashed rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #38bdf8; /* Cyber blue accent */
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-top: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }
        .info {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1); /* Subtle purple glow */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 5px solid #8b5cf6;
            margin: 30px 0;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 15px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05);
        }
        .info h2 {
            color: #a78bfa;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .info p {
            color: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .info strong {
            color: #a78bfa;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .mission-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
        }
        .mission-item:hover {
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.05);
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Sahyadri College of Engineering and Management</h1>
       
        <div class="section">
            <h2>College Vision</h2>
            <p>To be a premier institution in Technology and Management by fostering excellence in education, innovation, incubation and values to inspire and empower the young minds.</p>
           
            <h2>College Mission</h2>
            <div class="mission-item">📖 Creating an academic ambience to impart holistic education focusing on individual growth, integrity, ethical values and social responsibility.</div>
            <div class="mission-item">📖 Develop skill based learning through industry-institution interaction to enhance competency and promote entrepreneurship.</div>
            <div class="mission-item font-fix">📖 Fostering innovation and creativity through competitive environment with state-of-the-art infrastructure.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="info">
            <h2>Student Details</h2>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong> Sandesh</p>
            <p><strong>USN:</strong> 4sf23cs188</p>
            <p><strong>Department:</strong> CSE (Computer Science and Engineering)</p>
            <p><strong>Section:</strong> 7C</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Department Vision</h2>
            <p>To be a globally recognized center for imparting quality technical education through innovative research and incubation with moral values in the field of computer science and engineering.</p>
           
            <h2>Department Mission</h2>
            <div class="mission-item">📖 Fostering effective education through internal collaboration with industries to address societal demands.</div>
            <div class="mission-item">📖 Empowering professionals with strong ethical values and leadership abilities.</div>
            <div class="mission-item">📖 Developing research and entrepreneurship culture in students and faculty to cultivate lifelong learning.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
